939
01:14:14,826 --> 01:14:18,246
<i>Somebody said world peace
was in our hands,</i>

940
01:14:18,329 --> 01:14:21,166
<i>but all I did was play Ping-Pong.</i>

941
01:14:21,207 --> 01:14:24,294
When I got home,
I was a national celebrity.

942
01:14:25,003 --> 01:14:27,297
Famouser even than Captain Kangaroo.

943
01:14:27,380 --> 01:14:30,049
<i>Here he is, Forrest Gump, right here.</i>

944
01:14:36,806 --> 01:14:38,558
<i>Mr. Gump, have a seat.</i>

945
01:14:41,060 --> 01:14:43,229
<i>Forrest Gump, John Lennon.</i>

946
01:14:43,897 --> 01:14:45,550
<i>- Welcome home.
- You had quite a trip.</i>

947
01:14:45,560 --> 01:14:48,897
<i>Can you tell us, what was China like?</i>

948
01:14:51,821 --> 01:14:57,076
<i>In the land of China,
people hardly got nothing at all.</i>

949
01:14:57,160 --> 01:14:58,745
<i>No possessions?</i>

950
01:15:01,372 --> 01:15:04,584
<i>And in China, they never go to church.</i>

951
01:15:05,877 --> 01:15:07,587
<i>No religion, too?</i>

952
01:15:09,506 --> 01:15:12,800
<i>- Hard to imagine.
